The '''''Nova Crystal''''' was a [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] civilian [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]] in service during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. It [[Mission to the Corellian-Perlemian Intersection|fired]] upon and destroyed the [[Traffic Interdiction Vessel]] [[TIV Z590/1]], which it had mistakenly identified as a [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] vessel.

Due to the secrecy of the TIV's mission, the true nature of this vessel as a Republic ship was never released and the skipper of the ''Nova Crystal'' was regarded as a hero for his actions by the [[Perlemian Traffic Control]].

